00:03:22.199 --> 00:03:24.599 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Proszę pani, to dobry film?
- Nie nudny.

00:03:32.759 --> 00:03:35.280 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- A, o czym?
- O miłości, ale nudny.

00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:42.039 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
