00:49:58.000 --> 00:50:00.000 line:85% position:50% size:80%
[brzęk monety]

00:50:03.000 --> 00:50:05.000 line:85% position:50% size:80%
[terkotanie tarczy]

00:50:10.840 --> 00:50:12.920 line:85% position:50% size:80%
To ja.

00:50:13.000 --> 00:50:14.920 line:85% position:50% size:80%
